t last Augustat Robert Redford's Sundance Symposium on Global Climate Change.andM;&quot;Reflections&quot; is one of several multimedia environmental pieces developed byInterNetwork, which also is producing reference and visualization materialfor a number of federal agencies.andP;  Stevens said he plans to show his work atthe Apple Worldwide Developers' Conference in San Jose, Calif., this week.andM;InterNetwork Inc. is located at 411 Seventh St., Del Mar, Calif.andP;  92014;(619) 755-0439.andP;  n</TEXT></DOC>